  "author": "silentoplayz (G30)",
  "description": "A dramatic theme inspired by a solar eclipse — deep darkness with a radiant corona gradient at its center. Dark mode features warm amber corona tones against near-black space. OLED mode intensifies the effect with true black surroundings and a concentrated golden ring. Light mode softens it into warm parchment tones with a gentle golden radiance. Her mode reimagines the eclipse with a rose-crimson corona. Every mode uses a radial gradient positioned slightly above center to create the celestial effect.",
